### Criar evento
POST http://localhost:3001/events
Content-Type: application/json

### Criar evento
POST http://localhost:3001/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Show de Rock",
  "description": "Um show incrível",
  "date": "2099-12-01T20:00:00.000Z",
  "location": "São Paulo - SP",
  "price": 80.00,
  "capacity": 200,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "organizer": "Yasmin"
}

### Listar todos os eventos
GET http://localhost:3001/events

### Buscar evento por id
GET http://localhost:3001/events/1

### Atualizar evento
PUT http://localhost:3001/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Show de Rock Atualizado"
}

### Verificar disponibilidade
GET http://localhost:3001/events/1/availability

### Deletar evento
DELETE http://localhost:3001/events/1

### Criar inscrição
POST http://localhost:3001/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "registrationDate": "2099-11-01T10:00:00.000Z"
}

### Listar inscrições
GET http://localhost:3001/registrations

### Buscar inscrição por id
GET http://localhost:3001/registrations/1

### Cancelar inscrição
DELETE http://localhost:3001/registrations/1